# These .desktop files are symlinked explicitly by the dotfiles ansible role
# (the parent directory is shared with system-installed .desktop files, so it
# can't be folded by stow). Keep stow from touching them to avoid conflicts
# between stow's relative symlinks and ansible's absolute ones.
^/\.local/share/applications/nvim\.desktop$
^/\.local/share/applications/nvidia-settings\.desktop$
